->                  |
->         _________|_________
->        |                   |
->    ACPI0017-0          ACPI0017-1
-> GP0/HB0/ACPI0016-0   GP1/HB1/ACPI0016-1
->    |          |        |           |
->   RP0        RP1      RP2         RP3
->    |          |        |           |
->  SW 0       SW 1     SW 2        SW 3
->  |   |      |   |    |   |       |   |
-> EP0 EP1    EP2 EP3  EP4  EP5    EP6 EP7
